sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant UI as Frontend Dashboard
  participant API as KPI Controller
  participant KPISvc as KPIService
  participant SNRepo as SensorNodeRepository
  participant ReadRepo as ReadingRepository
  participant PollRepo as PolluantRepository
  participant CfgRepo as SiteConfigRepository
  participant DB as MongoDB

  UI->>API: GET /api/kpi/summary?siteId&periodStart&periodEnd&zoneId?
  API->>KPISvc: calculate TD/EMJ/IPE/RCO2

  opt zoneId provided
    KPISvc->>SNRepo: findNodeIdsByZone(zoneId)
    SNRepo-->>KPISvc: nodeIdFilter[]
  end

  KPISvc->>PollRepo: load polluants + thresholds + limits
  KPISvc->>CfgRepo: load active site config (airflow, weights, targets)
  KPISvc->>ReadRepo: aggregate/count readings in period
  ReadRepo->>DB: queries on readings
  DB-->>ReadRepo: stats and counts
  ReadRepo-->>KPISvc: avg, min, max, breachCount, totalCount

  KPISvc-->>API: TD/EMJ/IPE/RCO2 payload
  API-->>UI: KPI cards + trends + compliance status

  Note over KPISvc: Comparaison aux normes utilise\nregulatoryLimit / warningThreshold